    • handleGeneralTrigger

      private void handleGeneralTrigger (QuestPlayer questPlayer, ActiveTrigger activeTrigger)
      This method handles the most commonly used type of trigger, which should simply add to the progress. Apart from adding the progress, this method checks for the triggers applyOn and the triggers worldName
      Parameters:
      questPlayer - is the QuestPlayer object, used to check the world of the player
      activeTrigger - is the trigger which we need in order to add progress to it
